<i>adjective</i>: 고지식하다 [고지시카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고지식하다 [고지시카다]</dt><br>
<dd>uncompromising; intractable; dyed-in-the-wool; set in one's ways</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 바르고 곧아 융통성이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality being simple and up-front, which reduces flexibility.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>